# Cloudflare Pages redirects/rewrites
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Note: With hash-based routing (e.g., /app/jobs/#/{jobId}/review),
# no server-side redirects are needed. The hash portion is never sent
# to the server, so all requests go to /app/jobs/ and routing is
# handled client-side.

# Referral links: /r/CODE → landing page with ?ref=CODE
# The ReferralCapture component on the landing page stores the code in a cookie.
# This avoids the static export limitation with dynamic routes.
/r/* /en/?ref=:splat 302
